 DOCUMENT 4: GPT Integration & Synthesis Specification  
Growth Velocity Calculator — AI-Powered Strategic Analysis

Context: What GPT Synthesis Does  
The GPT synthesis layer transforms raw calculation results into contextual strategic insights by combining:

Hard Math: Calculated deltas, pressure indicators, benchmarks  
Soft Context: Agency Snapshot qualitative data (acquisition model, founder role, delivery structure)  
Coaching Frameworks: Project knowledge from AE Ladder, Growth Mastery materials  
Business Intelligence: Industry benchmarks, healthy ranges, pattern recognition

The Goal: Make the calculator feel like a strategic advisor, not just a math engine.

Two Synthesis Modes  
Mode 1: Single Scenario Analysis (Tab 1\)  
Purpose: Interpret one growth scenario with context  
Key Sections:

Reality Check — Feasibility assessment using Snapshot context  
Capacity Warning — Operational implications and bottlenecks  
One Big Lever — Highest-leverage improvement opportunity  
Watch-Outs — Active pressure family alerts with specific guidance

Tone: Observational, non-prescriptive, business-aware

Mode 2: Comparative Analysis (Tab 2, Pro Tier)  
Purpose: Compare 2-3 scenarios and explain trade-offs  
Key Sections:

Scenario Summary — Quick overview of each path  
Trade-Off Analysis — What each scenario optimizes for vs. what it sacrifices  
Strategic Verdict — Which dimensions favor which scenario  
Path Selection Guidance — Questions to help user choose

Tone: Comparative, trade-off focused, decision-supportive

