## **DESIGN SPECIFICATIONS**

### **Visual Hierarchy**

* Use Tailwind CSS v4.0 for all styling  
* shadcn/ui components: Card, Input, Select, Button, Table, Switch, Accordion  
* Consistent with Agency Snapshot and Clarity Compass sections  
* Professional, calm aesthetic (tool interface, not marketing)

### **Form Fields**

* Labels: Medium font weight, clear hierarchy  
* Inputs: shadcn/ui components with proper focus states  
* Helper text: Light gray, smaller font (text-sm)  
* Tooltips: Info icon (ℹ️) next to labels where needed  
* Currency inputs: Prefix with $ symbol  
* Percentage inputs: Suffix with % symbol  
* Read-only fields: Lighter background, disabled appearance

### **Layout**

* **Input Section:**  
  * Two-column layout (50/50 split) for Current State | Target State  
  * Advanced Features spans full width  
  * Max-width container, centered  
* **Output Section:**  
  * Full-width container  
  * Metric cards: 3 columns desktop, 2 tablet, 1 mobile  
  * Pressure cards: 3 columns desktop, 2 tablet, 1 mobile  
  * Charts: 2 columns desktop, 1 mobile  
  * Table: Full-width, horizontally scrollable on mobile

### **Spacing**

* Generous padding between sections (mb-8, mb-12)  
* Form fields: mb-4 or mb-6  
* Section headings: mb-6  
* Card grids: gap-6  
* Button groups: gap-4

### **Colors**

* Neutral palette (grays for backgrounds, text)  
* Single brand accent for CTAs (blue/primary)  
* Status colors: Green (`#22c55e`), Yellow (`#eab308`), Red (`#ef4444`), Gray (`#9ca3af`)  
* Subtle borders, no harsh lines  
* Info banners: Light blue background (`#dbeafe`)  
* Warning banners: Light yellow background (`#fef3c7`)

### **Typography**

* Headings: font-semibold, text-lg to text-2xl  
* Labels: font-medium, text-sm  
* Body text: font-normal, text-base  
* Helper text: font-normal, text-sm, text-gray-600  
* Metric values: font-bold, text-3xl to text-5xl

### **Responsive Behavior**

* Input section: Stacks vertically on mobile (Current State → Target State)  
* Metric/Pressure cards: 3 cols → 2 cols → 1 col  
* Charts: 2 cols → 1 col  
* Table: Horizontal scroll on mobile  
* Buttons: Stack vertically on mobile

